---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="The terms governing enquiries through this website and the basis on which Cyphral provides Cyber Essentials readiness consulting."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-[1600px] px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-16 pt-4 md:pt-8 pb-8 md:pb-12">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-maroon-700">
        Terms
      </p>
      <h1 class="mt-6 font-display text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-semibold text-navy-900 leading-[1.05] tracking-tight">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-neutral-600">
        Last updated: 22 June 2026
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BODY -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-[1600px] px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-16 pb-16 md:pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-base md:text-lg text-neutral-800 leading-relaxed">

      <h2 class="mt-4 font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-navy-900 leading-tight tracking-tight">
        About these terms
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-justify hyphens-auto">
        These terms govern enquiries made through this website and the basis on which Cyphral provides its services. They do not themselves form a contract for any specific engagement; each engagement is agreed separately in writing.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-12 font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-navy-900 leading-tight tracking-tight">
        Our services
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-justify hyphens-auto">
        Cyphral provides Cyber Essentials readiness consulting: we help businesses prepare for the Cyber Essentials scheme.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-justify hyphens-auto">
        Cyphral is a readiness consultant only. We are not an accredited Certification Body and we do not issue or award Cyber Essentials certification. Certification is carried out by IASME and its accredited Certification Bodies. The IASME assessment fee is separate from our fees and is paid directly to the Certification Body.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-12 font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-navy-900 leading-tight tracking-tight">
        Enquiries and no obligation
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-justify hyphens-auto">
        Sending an enquiry does not create a contract or oblige either party to proceed. Work begins only once scope and price are agreed in writing.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-12 font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-navy-900 leading-tight tracking-tight">
        Fees and payment
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-justify hyphens-auto">
        Fees for each engagement are set out in a written proposal before work begins. The IASME assessment fee is not included in our fees. Payment terms are agreed per engagement.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-justify hyphens-auto">
        We do not offer or recommend interest-bearing (riba) financing in any engagement.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-12 font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-navy-900 leading-tight tracking-tight">
        Scope and your responsibilities
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-justify hyphens-auto">
        Our readiness work depends on accurate information and timely cooperation from you. Implementing recommendations and maintaining controls remains your responsibility.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-12 font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-navy-900 leading-tight tracking-tight">
        Limitation of liability
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-justify hyphens-auto">
        We provide readiness consulting in good faith and to a professional standard, but we do not guarantee any particular certification outcome, which is determined solely by the Certification Body. To the extent permitted by law, our liability is limited to the fees paid for the relevant engagement. Nothing in these terms limits liability that cannot be limited by law.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-12 font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-navy-900 leading-tight tracking-tight">
        Governing law
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-justify hyphens-auto">
        These terms are governed by the law of England and Wales.
      </p>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
